OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FKeir Starmer is facing another
OL,7,Fbruising day in Parliament over the
OL,8,Fscandal surrounding Peter Mandelson's
OL,9,Fappointment as US ambassador, as
OL,10,FDonald Trump weighed in, appearing to
OL,11,Fgive the prime minister support.
OL,13,FOlly Robbins will have a chance to
OL,14,Frespond to the prime minister, who
OL,15,Fblamed the sacked senior civil servant
OL,16,Ffor "deliberately" keeping him in the
OL,17,Fdark over Lord Mandelson's failure to
OL,18,Fpass security vetting checks before
OL,19,Ftaking the Washington DC posting.
OL,26,@xD@EOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
