OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FThe House of Commons will subject the
OL,7,Fprime minister's latest efforts to lay
OL,8,Fout the facts of the scandal to
OL,9,Ffurther scrutiny on Tuesday, as MPs
OL,10,Fhold an emergency debate on
OL,11,FMandelson's appointment.
OL,13,FRobbins, until last week the most
OL,14,Fsenior civil servant in the Foreign
OL,15,FOffice, will reportedly tell the
OL,16,FForeign Affairs Committee that the
OL,17,Fgovernment pressured him into clearing
OL,18,FMandelson, despite the peer's
OL,19,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,20,FJeffrey Epstein, and business links to
OL,21,FRussia and China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
