OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FAhead ot Robbins's appearance, Energy
OL,7,FSecretary Ed Miliband said both he and
OL,8,Fthen foreign secretary David Lammy had
OL,9,Fhad concerns about Mandelson's
OL,10,Fappointment.
OL,12,FHe told Sky News Mandelson should
OL,13,Fnever have been appointed and added:
OL,14,F"I steered well clear of Peter
OL,15,FMandelson when I became Labour leader
OL,16,Fin 2010."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FHe went on to say: "I had a
OL,7,Fconversation with David Lammy about it
OL,8,Fbefore the appointment, and I said I
OL,9,Fwas worried about it, I think he was
OL,10,Fworried about it too."
OL,12,FMandelson, who spent nine months as US
OL,13,Fambassador before fresh details of his
OL,14,Frelationship with Epstein emerged, was
OL,15,Fa political appointment to the plum
OL,16,Fdiplomatic role, rather than the
OL,17,FWashington job going to a career
OL,18,Fdiplomat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
