PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FThe repeated crisis of Mandelson's
OL,7,Fappointment has threatened to topple
OL,8,FStarmer's premiership several times,
OL,9,Fwith his own party frustrated by the
OL,10,Fcrisis and opposition parties
OL,11,Fdemanding he resign.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, the prime minister
OL,14,Fappeared to get backing from an
OL,15,Funlikely source, the US president.
OL,17,FHe wrote on his Truth Social platform:
OL,18,F"Prime Minister Keir Starmer of the
OL,19,FUnited Kingdom acknowledged that he
OL,20,F'exercised wrong judgement' when he
OL,21,Fchose his Ambassador to Washington.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
