PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,F"I agree, he was a really bad pick.
OL,7,FPlenty of time to recover, however!
OL,8,FPresident DJT."
OL,10,FTrump's latest comments are markedly
OL,11,Fdifferent from his recent ones about
OL,12,Fthe prime minister, which have
OL,13,Fcriticised his lack of support for the
OL,14,FUnited States' war with Iran.
OL,16,FTrump's support is unlikely to impress
OL,17,FMPs questioning Robbins on Tuesday.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
