OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FThe Times also reported that Robbins
OL,7,Fwill use his "box office" appearance
OL,8,Fat the committee to reveal he did not
OL,9,Fsee the formal recommendation by
OL,10,Fvetting officials that Mandelson
OL,11,Fshould not be given clearance, while
OL,12,Finsisting the UK Security Vetting
OL,13,F(UKSV) process is only advisory.
OL,15,FOn Monday, the prime minister said he
OL,16,Fchallenged Robbins over why he went
OL,17,Fagainst the recommendation of UKSV.
OL,19,F"I did ask him and I didn't accept his
OL,20,Fexplanation," Starmer told the
OL,21,FCommons. "That's why I sacked him."
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@YO]{D@AOU|D@MO]}D@JOU}D@cO]
