OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe prime minister also said he would
OL,12,Fnot have appointed Mandelson if he had
OL,13,Fknown the peer had failed the checks
OL,14,Fand insisted there was no pressure
OL,15,Ffrom No 10 to push through the high-
OL,16,Fprofile appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
