OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776773466
OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Fapplied for the emergency Commons
OL,8,Fdebate about the scandal, telling MPs
OL,9,Fit was "a matter of national security
OL,10,Fbecause the prime minister has
OL,11,Fadmitted appointing a known serious
OL,12,Fsecurity risk to our most sensitive
OL,13,Fdiplomatic post".
OL,15,FIt is not known which minister will
OL,16,Fappear at the debate on behalf of the
OL,17,Fgovernment.
