OL,3,CStarmer to face second bruising day as
OL,4,CTrump weighs in on Mandelson affair
OL,6,FStarmer said in his appearance in the
OL,7,FCommons on Monday afternoon that the
OL,8,Fgovernment was investigating security
OL,9,Fconcerns relating to Mandelson's time
OL,10,Fas US ambassador.
OL,12,FHe also said the terms of a probe into
OL,13,Fgovernment security vetting have been
OL,14,Fupdated in light of the latest
OL,15,Frevelations about Mandelson and the
OL,16,Finquiry will be led by Sir Adrian
OL,17,FFulford, a senior judge and chairman
OL,18,Fof the Southport Inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
